Have a happy new year!! 🎉From Orlando Florida! I can't wait to spend another amazing year with you!!😘❤
What a magnificent dinner at Dakota's in Dallas, TX. What a beautiful site, and the restaurant was beautiful too;) I loved every second of this date. I would replay every moment of it❤️

Roughly 3 years ago I saw this beautiful girl, that day I first shook her hand and introduced myself I gazed upon her eyes and knew this girl was special. 6 months later I asked her on a date. Then after 6 months of dates then and there we made it official:) ever since then my life has changed in every best way possible. When I wake up I know no matter what it's going to be a good day just because in the back of my mind I know that I still have the best girlfriend in the world and I couldn't be any happier. Thank you for making these past few years the best years of my life❤️😘

Spending the 4th of July with this girl couldn't be any more amazing:) even though we didn't pop any fireworks we still went on an amazing date and saw a cool movie. Thank you for spending 4 of July with me honey🙂❤️
To the one and only my best friend❤️ I just can't believe you are 19! You are not only an amazing girlfriend and make me the happiest man in the world you are my best friend 😘🎊🎉🎂

Wow... i cant believe she finally graduated:) im so blessed to have to an amazing girlfriend like her in my life, first of all shes super smart, shes stunningly beautiful, she is just the whole package. Any man would be so greatful to have her in their lives and i guess im just that lucky fella:) just her smile can brighten up the world and her knowledge and kindness will one day make a huge impact on everyones life is she hasn't already. Now seeing her done with high school and going off to college brings a tear to my eye as we start a new chapter together not only with God but a couple. Camille i just wanna say how proud i am of you and far you have gotten. Thanks for everything that you have done in my life and i cant wait to spend more memorable events with you. So once again congratulations best friend😊😘💕

div.span: Words cannot describe how I feel. On March 13th, 2020, I married my best friend who has always been there for me. About six years ago I met this incredibly gorgeous woman and I knew from the first time I laid my eyes on her that I had to be with her. After getting to know her I knew I couldn’t live life without her. I’m so happy to spend the rest of my life with her. Thank you to everyone who came to celebrate this amazing day. I love you @wolfgirl212 and I can’t wait to see what journeys lie ahead.
